End goal:
Be able to call a function that takes a
directory and a PEG that might replace
text in the files in the directory,
and then save those files.

replace-in-files


OK Goal 1:
OK 0. Apply PEG to a string
OK 1. Apply PEG to a file
OK 2. Replace the contents of that file
      with the result of the PEG

replace-in-file

Goal 2:
1. Find all files in directory
   and subdirectories
2. Run replace-in-file on all those files

